            <h2>About</h2>
            <p>This is a sample web application that shows some of the features and concepts covered in the 70-487 exam.</p>
            <p>
                For more information, see
                <a href="https://hendrikbulens.wordpress.com/2016/06/04/preparation-guide-for-exam-70-487-developing-microsoft-azure-and-web-services/" target="_blank">
                    this series of blog posts.
                </a>
            </p>

            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://hendrikbulens.wordpress.com/2016/06/04/exam-70-487-preparation-part-i-accessing-data/" target="_blank">Part I: Accessing Data</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://hendrikbulens.wordpress.com/2016/06/04/exam-70-487-preparation-part-ii-entity-framework/" target="_blank">Part II: Entity Framework</a></li>
