                <li><a href="https://hendrikbulens.wordpress.com/2016/06/04/exam-70-487-preparation-part-v-deployment/" target="_blank">Part V: Deployment</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6">
            <h2>Getting started</h2>
            <p>In order to use this website to its full extent, you need to run the following programs:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Web API console application <b>[hbulens.Exam70487.WebApi]</b></li>
                <li>WCF console application <b>[hbulens.Exam70487.Wcf]</b></li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                Also make sure you have created a database that matches the schema as specified in the Entity Data Model.
                You can use the <b>schema compare</b> tool SQL Server Data Tools project to update the database. There is also some sample data that you can use to populate the database.
            </p>
